    | I’m Don Osborne, a highly experienced and award winning UX design leader with over 15 years of experience creating intuitive, user-centered designs that drive business success. 
    | I’ve managed designers from around the world and strive to bring out the best in my team members. 
    | If you think I would be a good fit for your project, 
    a(href="/contact/")
      | get in touch
    | . Thanks!

